and win _ I was just thankful. I was just happy.''
</P>
<P>
   Oh, they complained about Turn 2. Too tight. And they bemoaned
the lack of a second groove to race in.
</P>
<P>
   Few drivers ever traveled two abreast. And passing opponents is
still somewhat of an Indiana Jones adventure.
</P>
<P>
   But it didn't spoil the show. Rather, let me suggest, the
track's contrariness enhanced it.
</P>
<P>
   ``The changes they've made here were a big improvement,''
Labonte said. ``You saw people race real good today, compared to
