their daughters' salvation.
 &HT;    Reporters repeatedly commented on their deep faith with one
saying, ``If you miss faith in this story, you miss the story.''
 &HT;    It was impossible to miss the faith story in a Bible-belt town
like Memphis. Sadly, however, the faith presented by the parents
