 &HT;    If we wait and listen, allowing suffering to shape our souls,
then we will not have facile answers.
 &HT;    I, too, feel certain those little girls are safe in God.
Perhaps, however, this was not the moment to say so. Perhaps we all
need to live with the sorrow and mystery of untimely death to
