 &HT;    Who can say what could come from such tragedy? I do not know and
pray I will never know from personal experience.
 &HT;    I do know, however, that we would all be better off if not
victimized by bad theology that bypasses human pain.
 &HT;    
 &HT;    ----
 &HT;    c.1999 Diana Butler Bass
