 &HT;    This fundamental theological insight _ that suffering brings
forth new life _ is adult faith. Although hard to believe, once it
is embraced, we find true freedom.
 &HT;    As the old hymn reminds us, ``He is risen! Death is conquered,
we are free!''
 &HT;    
 &HT;    ----
 &HT;    
 &HT;    c.1999 Diana Butler Bass
<TEXT>
