Tokyo and down 1.1 in Hong Kong. They rose 1.4 percent in
Frankfurt, 1.4 percent in London, 0.1 percent in Brazil and 1.2
percent in Mexico. On the American debt market, the long bond was
down 17/32 point at midday. By Kenneth N. Gilpin.
