March 30. If you have any questions, please call Patricia Hardin on
the Star's News Desk at (816) 234-4753. METH-MAN (Kansas City, Mo.)
_ The biggest, baddest meth dealer in Jackson County, Mo., history
looked neither big nor bad. Willi Olsen looked old and tired, with
gray hair and weathered skin the color of ash. He was only 48, but
