whether to raise the fuel tax to help finance a new transportation
plan. Already gasoline prices have been going up, and now comes the
idea of a 5-cent-a-gallon gas tax increase in Kansas. That would
make the Kansas tax 6 cents higher than in Missouri. By JOHN A.
