   TECH-MEDIA _ The Internet is becoming an increasingly big part
in both the marketing and distribution of music. (Haddad, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   MAC-REPORT _ Apple Computer is hoping its popular new iMac
computer will lure developers back to the Mac platform. (Haddad ,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   TECH-REPORT _ The folks at Yahoo! Internet Life have a standing
feature that takes a look at whether electronic commerce is really
the wave of the future. The piece in the April issue discusses the
question of whether it is easier to buy something on the Internet
or the old-fashioned way. (Clothier, Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
MOVED.
